dc_title_s: Geologic map of the Williams Hill quadrangle, Monterey County, California
dc_description_s: by Thomas W. Dibblee, Jr. ; edited by John A. Minch. Relief shown by contours and spot heights. "Topographic base map from available USGS 7.5-minute quadrangle Williams Hill CA 1949. Photorevised 1979. AMS 1755 I NE, series V895." "First printing, May 2006." Includes quadrangle location map, index to adjacent 7.5 minute quadrangles, and index to sources of geology. Includes "pertinent references", most recent 1979.
dc_publisher_s: Santa Barbara Museum of Natural History
